<th style="text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 8px;">0.99</th>
<th style="text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 8px;">0.999</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 8px; background: #f9fafb;">\(f(x)\ \rightarrow\)</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 6px; text-align: center;">
<div style="display: flex; gap: 6px; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"><input data-x="0.9" class="lx1-in" type="text" inputmode="decimal" style="width: 120px; padding: 6px 8px; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 8px;" /> <span class="lx1-ok" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">✅</span> <span class="lx1-bad" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">❌</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 6px; text-align: center;">
<div style="display: flex; gap: 6px; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"><input data-x="0.99" class="lx1-in" type="text" inputmode="decimal" style="width: 120px; padding: 6px 8px; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 8px;" /> <span class="lx1-ok" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">✅</span> <span class="lx1-bad" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">❌</span></div>
